    "We set the following core research questions: (1) What is the overall effect of project-based learning on improving students' CT abilities and in various dimensions?",
    "(2) How do the effects of PBL on enhancing the CT abilities of students vary across different levels in the K-12 stage?",
    "We employed a meta-analysis approach to delve deeper into these questions (Valls et al., 2022).",
    "Meta-analysis is a statistical method that concentrates on analyzing and synthesizing the results of many similar independent studies to provide a broader and more profound understanding.",
    "It reflects the effectiveness of research in a quantitative manner using original data [44]."
